            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Selaqui International School in Dehradun provides an exceptional CBSE education, fostering a strong sense of community and comprehensive development. From exceptional academics to a rich cultural environment, the school cultivates a strong sense of togetherness.\n\nWe've found Selaqui International School to be the ideal CBSE school in Dehradun, where academic excellence goes hand in hand with sports, cultural activities and extracurriculars in a nurturing, family-like atmosphere and  we, as parents, feel consistently connected.\n\nThe parental-like devotion of the Principal sir, house/ hostel mothers, teachers, administration staffs and  all the faculty members is deeply appreciated.\n\nI am and will always be  grateful to the school from the bottom of my heart for how it has helped to shape my child into a confident, considerate and responsible individual.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
