          "reviewBody": "It was an apt decision to choose… Selaqui for my kids. The school provides an overall development of a child… the Environment of the school is very positive. The teachers are very friendly and cooperative towards the children. Initially it is a task to get habituated to the Boarding life… but as the children explore the opportunities…they start enjoying the Boarding life….. My experience has been very satisfying and I recommend Selaqui International School for sure…..",
          "publisher": {
