            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Selaqui school is really worth it. It’s one of the finest boarding school. It gives holistic approach for the growth of the child and it focuses on both studies and sports. The campus is well maintained and has all facilities.They prepare the students from all aspects.",
          "publisher": {
