          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Selaqui International School - Selakui"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Nikhil Jawahar"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-03-07",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Two years ago, our son joined Selaqui International School in Class IX and is now appearing for his Class X board exams.\n\nWhen he joined, he was barely passing and had little interest in studies. His only goal was to pass. However, when I met him just before his exams, he told me he was aiming for 90% or more, which was a huge surprise for us. His approach and attitude towards studies have completely changed, and he has put in tremendous effort, supported by his teachers in class and hostel, along with the House Tutors.\n\nThe school provides a well-structured environment where every student is encouraged to focus on their tasks. The hostel stay is very well managed by the House Masters and their team.\n\nThere have been times when my son was unwell, and the on-campus doctor provided excellent medical care, ensuring a quick recovery.\n\nWe are incredibly grateful to the Headmaster, Mr. Rashid Sharfuddin, Pastoral Head, Mr. Ashford Lyonette, House Master, Mr. Satish Sah, the Academic Head, the Sports In-Charge, and the entire staff. A special mention goes to Mohan Ji, who takes care of the entire house. We truly appreciate their dedication and support.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Selaqui International School - Selakui"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sonal sharma"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-03-07",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Enrolling my son at Selaqui International School has been an ideal decision. The transition was seamless, and the supportive teachers have played a significant role in nurturing his growth. The school's strict anti-ragging policy ensures a safe and welcoming environment, allowing students to thrive. With a wide range of activities to choose from and a picturesque campus, Selaqui offers the perfect blend of academics and extracurricular opportunities.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
